dmca.title: A Little Dilution Goes A Long Way, Part 2
dmca.body:
Mr. XXXXX,

I appreciate that Surferz.net may not feel that the use of the business name Intellhost infringes upon or dilutes the famous Intel mark and I will attempt to more fully explain why this is in fact the case and respond to a number of misstatements of the law of trademarks contained in your previous e-mails.
